text: Matthew P. Denn (born February 9, 1966) is an American lawyer and politician. He was the 45th Attorney General of Delaware from 2015 until 2019. Denn was the 25th Lieutenant Governor of Delaware from 2009 to 2015. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Lieutenant Governors of Delaware Category:Lawyers from Delaware Category:Politicians from Wilmington, Delaware Category:Businesspeople from Wilmington, Delaware Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
